Teen Alyssa Hatcher steals money from her parents and uses it to try to have them killed. Joining Nancy Grace today: Attorney Brad Micklin, family law ; Dr. Jolie Silva,  Clinical and Forensic Psychologist;  Joe Scott Morgan Forensics Expert; Steven Lampley Former Detective; Levi Page, reporter.
